exclude=[1-9A-Za-fh-z]*.i?86 g[0-9A-Za-km-z]*.i?86 gl[0-9A-Za-hj-z]*.i?86 gli[0-9A-Zac-z]*.i?86 glib[0-9A-Za-bd-z]*.i?86
